{
  "doc_id": "34123",
  "text": "Investigators have evaluated anakinra, an IL-1 inhibitor approved for the treatment of rheumatoid arthritis, in the treatment of AS. Conflicting reports are available on the efficacy of anakinra in the management of AS. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Hence, larger clinical trials are required for drawing any conclusions about its efficacy.",
